CAM Director Amoros Pledges Court Fight for Pension, Efe Says

-- B y   B e n   S i l l s
-- 
2011-10-04T06:29:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/cam-director-amoros-pledges-court-fight-for-pension-efe-says.html
The former general director of  Caja
de Ahorros del Mediterraneo (CAM)  Maria Dolores Amoros pledged to take
legal action to claim her annual pension payment of 370,000
euros ($489,000) after being fired by the lender’s
administrators, Efe newswire reported.  Amoros said her management of the lender has been “honest,
correct, transparent and within the law,” the newswire
reported.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
